se they can find high-paying, flexible technical work at top companies like=
 Nike and Porsche and <strong>pay no fee</strong> on what they earn. They c=
an quit their full-time jobs, get as much work as they want, and log off wh=
en they want.&nbsp;</p></li></ul><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">The fact that they can also earn =
